{"tid":646023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港其實有冇人口上限","createTime":"2018-04-28T16:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T16:58:08.000Z","uid":183567,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e072bd7fbe9870942c1243f270507328d6e08e39","tid":646023,"uid":183567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:29:29.000Z","msg":"都已經唔好講咩人口入侵問題同啲人本身引發嘅問題<br />\n印度人 南亞人 大陸人 黑人 白人都居留<br />\n日日地鐵都迫爆 其實係咪已經overloaded<br />\n個政府係咪應該做下野 唔通要比香港人口上2000萬咩 <br />\n同堔圳拎下地都好呀 返正佢地周圍食地<br />\n比外來人口攞褔利都唔係問題 但到底有無人口管制"},{"pid":"7cbee825d3bdc9805be87dfce7571787c10c8b28","tid":646023,"uid":50856,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:32:11.000Z","msg":"問題係低技術工作請唔到人"},{"pid":"2ebb1f9d0b995239e975ad608c2a2f12c579b341","tid":646023,"uid":183592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:40:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問題係低技術工作請唔到人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講真，政府對某階層咁眷顧，做乜鬼呀，日日屋邨撚雀 月月清幾撚happy ，又有屋住，政府驚果班友發起窮惡仲難攪 ，依家邊有人咁樣樣做野呀，做愛生仔拎福利，幾撚開心。"},{"pid":"c8e1481976d49f9082aaac6733f2022867a9e3fd","tid":646023,"uid":183567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cbee825d3bdc9805be87dfce7571787c10c8b28","tid":646023,"uid":50856,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:32:11.000Z","msg":"問題係低技術工作請唔到人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲無人做嘅行業人工都開始上啦 都多左後生仔做工人<br />\n但外地人就好似無少過入口咁"},{"pid":"bd5c87c5f0522b444ff660d08b1141dd903204d6","tid":646023,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:48:14.000Z","msg":"不斷引人入嚟已經好on9，香港不嬲地少人多<br />\n仲要引晒啲垃圾蝗蝻入嚟搶公屋搶福利先最on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6218f85d61124f33865ced919234d7e88e6104b7","tid":646023,"uid":183567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0